# ==============================================================================
# OpenVPN PKI – Git Ignore Rules
# ==============================================================================
#
# Purpose
# - Prevent private keys and sensitive cryptographic material from being
#   committed to version control.
# - Allow public certificates required for infrastructure provisioning.
#
# NEVER commit:
# - Private keys
# - TLS auth keys
# - CSR / EasyRSA working files
# ==============================================================================

# --- Private key material (NEVER commit) ---
pki/private/
pki/reqs/
pki/inline/
pki/ta.key
pki/index.txt*
pki/serial*
pki/*.old
pki/*.bak

# --- Allow public / safe material ---
!pki/ca.crt
!pki/issued/
!pki/dh.pem
